OL,3,CJudge who jailed rioters after
OL,4,Cstabbings reveals he received threats
OL,6,FHe said: "The reaction has been
OL,7,Foverwhelmingly positive. There have
OL,8,Fbeen some twits online who have posted
OL,9,Fall sorts of daft things about me and
OL,10,Fsome pretty unpleasant threats have
OL,11,Fbeen made towards me and the family.
OL,13,F"The odd dodgy package has arrived at
OL,14,Fthe court containing threats towards
OL,15,Fme. But that, I'm afraid, goes with
OL,16,Fthe territory of the job."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
