OL,3,CJudge who jailed rioters after
OL,4,Cstabbings reveals he received threats
OL,6,FJudge Menary said so far in Liverpool
OL,7,Fthere had been sentences for more than
OL,8,F50 people who were involved in
OL,9,Frioting, which broke out in Southport
OL,10,Fand later spread to Liverpool and
OL,11,Facross the country after the knife
OL,12,Fattack in which three girls were
OL,13,Fkilled on 29 July.
OL,15,FHe said his favourite post came from a
OL,16,Fsocial media user in Texas, USA, who
OL,17,Fwrote: "The UK has fallen to savages.
OL,18,FThe dude with the dead squirrel on his
OL,19,Fhead has just confirmed it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
