OL,3,CJudge who jailed rioters after
OL,4,Cstabbings reveals he received threats
OL,6,FThanking those working in the
OL,7,Femergency services, the judge said:
OL,8,F"It's been a busy few weeks but
OL,9,Fnothing compared to the pressure that
OL,10,Fso many of you and your colleagues
OL,11,Fhave experienced and regularly
OL,12,Fexperience day in and day out."
OL,14,FThe annual National 999 Day service,
OL,15,Fat Liverpool Parish Church, was
OL,16,Fattended by leaders from the city's
OL,17,Ffaith communities as well as members
OL,18,Fof the emergency services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
