OL,3,CJudge who jailed rioters after
OL,4,Cstabbings reveals he received threats
OL,6,FUK Children's Laureate Frank Cottrell-
OL,7,FBoyce spoke along with Deborah Moore,
OL,8,Fthe manager of Spellow Hub library
OL,9,Fwhich was set on fire during disorder
OL,10,Fon County Road in Liverpool, and Alex
OL,11,FMcCormick, who raised more than
OL,12,F#250,000 to repair the library.
OL,14,FThe children's author said the good in
OL,15,Fthe city outweighed the bad, but
OL,16,Fadded: "We've learned this summer,
OL,17,Fsurely, that the good needs to be
OL,18,Fdefended and it needs to be vigilant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
