OL,3,CJudge who jailed rioters after
OL,4,Cstabbings reveals he received threats
OL,6,F"Its defenders are here in this church
OL,7,Ftoday, its defenders are you. I wanted
OL,8,Fto take this opportunity to say a
OL,9,Fmassive thank you to you for defending
OL,10,Fand looking out for the good."
OL,12,FLord Mayor of Liverpool Richard Kemp
OL,13,Ftold emergency workers said: "You are
OL,14,Fthe people who, when there is a
OL,15,Fproblem, run into it while the rest of
OL,16,Fus run from it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
